videoPlayer

Class MenuBar

  • java.lang.Object
    • videoPlayer.MenuBar

  • public class MenuBar
extends java.lang.Object
    A menu bar for a video player. Has options to open and close video files. Option to quit the program. Options to play, pause, stop, rewind, fast forward, and resize. Help menu contains documentation and about option. Each menu item can have an event handler given to it. The edit menu can be disabled, as well as the open and close options.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Steven Proctor
